description: Modern sophistication meets South Boston charm! This expansive 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom 2019 residence offers 1,466 sq ft of thoughtfully designed living space, complete with private elevator access, two balconies, and garage parking. An entertainer’s dream, the open-concept layout features a chef’s kitchen with a sleek waterfall island, custom bar, gas fireplace, and balcony. The generous primary suite boasts a private balcony, office nook, and a walk-in closet with flexibility for a fitness area or nursery. Elevated with Thermador and Bosch appliances, beautiful hardwood floors, soaring ceilings, oversized windows, and built-in Sonos sound system. Washer/dryer in unit. This home combines ultimate comfort with unmatched convenience—just moments from neighborhood dining, shops, Carson Beach, the South End, and easy transit via the Red Line and local bus routes. An ideal offering for both homeowners and investors alike. Open House Sat 9/13 & Sun 9/14 from 1 - 2:30 PM
